<div class="hisui-layout" fit="true">
	<div data-options="region:'north',border:false,collapsible:false,headerCls:'panel-header-gray',iconCls:'icon-reset'" style="height:125px;">
		<div class="hisui-panel" style="border:0;border-bottom:1px solid #ccc;border-radius:0;">
			<div class="c-search">
				<div class="c-row">
					<span style="color:red;">数据类型</span>
					<input class='hisui-radio' label='医嘱模板' type="radio" id="OrdTempDataType" name="HandleDataType" value="OrdTemp"/>
					<input class='hisui-radio' label='诊断模板' type="radio" id="DiaTempDataType" name="HandleDataType" value="DiaTemp"/>
					<input class='hisui-radio' label='医嘱套' type="radio" id="ARCOSDataType" name="HandleDataType" value="ARCOS"/>
					<input class='hisui-radio' label='用户常用用法' type="radio" id="UserFavDataType" name="HandleDataType" value="UserFav"/>
				</div>
				<div class="c-row">
					
					<span>科室</span>
					<input id="FCTLocName" style="width:150px;"></input><input type="hidden" id="FCTLocID"></input>
	        		<!--<IMG id="11" name="111" style="margin-left:-25px;" src="../images/websys/lookup.gif" onclick="FCTLoc_lookuphandler()">-->
					<span class="c-span2"></span>
					<input class='hisui-radio' label='按科室查询' type="radio" id="Departments" name="OperType" value="Departments"/>
					
					<span class="c-span5">文件</span>
					<input class="hisui-filebox" type="file" id="TemplateExcel" name="FileStream" data-options="width:250,buttonText:'选择'">
					<!--
					<span class="filebox" style="width: 175px; height: 28px;">
						<a href="javascript:;" class="filebox-button filebox-button-right l-btn l-btn-small">
						<span class="l-btn-left"><span class="l-btn-text">选择</span></span>
							<label class="filebox-label" for="TemplateExcel"></label>
						</a>
							<input class="filebox-text" autocomplete="off" readonly="readonly" placeholder="" 
								style="width: 112px; height: 28px; line-height: 28px; margin-left: 0px;">
							<input type="file" class="filebox-value" id="TemplateExcel">
					</span>
					-->
					<span class="c-span2"></span>
					<a class="hisui-linkbutton"  data-options="iconCls:'icon-w-find'" id="FindButton">查询</a>
					<span class="c-span2"></span>
					<a class="hisui-linkbutton" type="button"  data-options="iconCls:'icon-w-import'" id="Import">导入</a>
				</div>
				<div class="c-row">
					<span>用户</span>
					<input type="text" id="FUserName" style="width:150px;"></input><input type="hidden" id="FUserID"></input>
	        		<!--<IMG id="22" name="222"style="margin-left:-25px;"  src="../images/websys/lookup.gif" onclick="FUser_lookuphandler()">-->
					<span class="c-span2"></span>
					<input class='hisui-radio' label='按用户查询' type="radio" id="Personal" name="OperType" value="Personal"/>	
					<span class="c-span5">AppKey</span>
					<input type="text" class="hisui-validatebox" id="AppKey" style="width:245px;" />
					<span class="c-span2"></span>
					<a class="hisui-linkbutton"  data-options="iconCls:'icon-w-clean'" id="resetButton">清屏</a>
					<span class="c-span2"></span>
					<a class="hisui-linkbutton"  data-options="iconCls:'icon-w-export'" id="Export">导出</a>
					<a id="DownLoad" href="#" style="display:none;">download</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	
	<div data-options="region:'center',title:'',border:false">
			<table id="DateTable"></table>													
			<div title="主页" id="Instructions" >   
				<div class="tpl2">
					<div class="hisui-panel c-panel" title="查询" data-options="fit:true,collapsible:false">
						<ul>
							<li>1. 选择：科室模板或个人模板,不选则默认查询所有数据</li>
							<li>2. 当选择按科室查询时,必须选择某个科室</li>
							<li>3. 当选择按个人查询,必须选择某个用户</li>
							<li class="last">4. 若知道AppKey(医嘱模板)，则可以输入进行查询</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="tpl2">
					<div class="hisui-panel c-panel" title="导入" data-options="fit:true,collapsible:false">
						<ul>
							<li>1. 可按导出的模板内容收集数据,注意标注*号列</li>
							<li>2. 导入内容完全按照excel内容,与界面查询条件无关</li>
							<li>3. excel中若部分数据导入失败,不会整体回滚,请注意二次导入产生的垃圾数据</li>
							<li class="last">4. 仅支持xls或xlsx两种格式</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="tpl2">
					<div class="hisui-panel c-panel" title="导出" data-options="fit:true,collapsible:false">
						<ul>
							<li>1.参照查询说明</li>
							<li>2.可直接选择条件导出,无需先在界面查询出数据</li>
							<li class="last">3. 导出时直接下载数据库内容,与界面查询出来的数据无关。</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>   
	</div>
</div>